commit 0a654410190551b77c610cf0f8cd03df37dc012a
Author: Gustaf Neumann <neumann@wu-wien.ac.at>
Date:   2025-03-28

    Added defaults to configuration parameters to shorten required configuration section
    
    In particular, the following configuration parameters git defaults:
    - relaydomains: localhost
    - localdomains: localhost
    - initproc: smtpd::init
    - rcptproc: smtpd::rcpt
    - dataproc: smtpd::data
    - errorproc: smtpd::error

